text:
There are unfortunately some problems with the build if it is performed from a
directory with multiple names due to symlinks.

e.g., on a normal Solaris install, /usr/src and /usr/share/src both resolve to
the same directory

until somebody figures out how to fix this, you need to build Apache from a
different directory

sorry!
